MAUI, HAWAII

Exclusive Europe Packages
With Northwest and KLM
Amsterdam Super Stay Package
Enjoy great savings with Northwest Airlines and KLM Royal
Dutch Airlines all-inclusive special air and land package for
travel from the United States to Amsterdam.
Amsterdam Program Package* price ranges from:
v $539 (select East Coast cities) to $699 (select West
Coast cities) for travel between November 1, 1996 and
January 12, 1997 and from February 21 through
March 15, 1997.
v Save an additional $100 for travel between January 13 and
February 20, 1997, when you purchase your tickets by
November 30, 1996.
v Program includes roundtrip Coach Class airfare on KLM
or Northwest Airlines from U.S. to Amsterdam, three
nights deluxe hotel accommodations, hotel service charges
and taxes, plus daily buffet breakfast.
• Additional hotel nights and optional Alamo rental car are
available at special rates.
*Prices are based on per person, double room occupancy. Travel is permitted
on NW/KL and NW Airlink flights only. Please add $100 roundtrip for
travel via Northwest Airlink flights 2900-3499/5021-5899. Price does not
include up to $50 in Passenger Facility charges/ international taxes, fees,
and surcharges. Travel may not originate between 12/13/96 - 1/12/97.
Northwest and KLM also offer special land programs for
our transatlantic passengers originating in the United
States and completing travel by March 31, 1997.
v Happy Holland Bargain Program provides special priced
hotel rates in Amsterdam when your travel itinerary
includes a stopover in Amsterdam.
v Passport to Europe Program offers special priced intra-
Europe air fares on KLM.
v Holland Fly/Drive Program offers a special priced
Alamo car rental in Amsterdam.
All programs must be purchased in the U.S. prior to travel in
conjunction with your Northwest/KLM transatlantic ticket,
and are subject to availability. Other restrictions apply.
Please call your travel agent or KLM at 1-800-3-747-747 for
complete details and reservations.
